1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,680
Ndikufuna kukuonetsani mmene mungafufuzire chilichonse chifukwa kufufuza ndi mphamvu.

2
00:00:05,680 --> 00:00:10,000
Komanso ndi luso ndipo mukaphunzira kuchita zimenezi, mukhoza kudziphunzitsa nokha.

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:11,000
chilichonse chimene mukufuna.

4
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:14,760
Ndipo ngati mutazindikira posachedwapa kuti anthu ambiri sadziwa kufufuza, iwo amadziwa momwe

5
00:00:14,760 --> 00:00:15,760
kuti tifufuze.

6
00:00:15,760 --> 00:00:19,880
Ndipo pali kusiyana kwakukulu chifukwa pamene inu kufufuza, inu kudalira ena

7
00:00:19,880 --> 00:00:22,440
anthu kuti akuganizireni ndipo sitikufuna zimenezo.

8
00:00:22,440 --> 00:00:23,840
Tikufuna kuchita bwino.

9
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:26,080
Chotero, inde, kafukufuku ali ndi miyezo yake.

10
00:00:26,080 --> 00:00:29,560
Dongosolo langa limene ndimagwiritsa ntchito lili ndi zinayi, choncho ndikuuzani zimene mungachite.

11
00:00:29,560 --> 00:00:31,680
Chimodzi ndi kufufuza kwanu.

12
00:00:31,680 --> 00:00:35,600
Apa ndi pamene muyenera kuyamba, koma apa ndi pamene anthu ambiri amaima.

13
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:41,760
Pano pali kufufuza kwanu pa Google, mavidiyo a TikTok, mafotokozedwe a YouTube, mayankho a AI.

14
00:00:41,760 --> 00:00:46,519
Ndipo vuto ndi kusiya pano ndi kuti inu kupeza oponderezedwa mfundo ndipo inu

15
00:00:46,519 --> 00:00:48,640
osadziŵa mmene anamangidwira.

16
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:49,640
Ndiye tiyeni titenge chitsanzo.

17
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:55,000
Tiyerekeze kuti mwafufuza zinthu zakuda ndipo mwapeza zotsatira ngati,

18
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:57,600
chimapanga 85% ya chilengedwe chonse.

19
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,760
Sitingachione.

20
00:00:58,760 --> 00:01:00,520
Zimakhudza mphamvu yokoka.

21
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:05,120
Mumapeza mfundo zonsezi, koma simukumvetsabe zinthu monga mmene tikudziwira kuti

22
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:11,440
Kodi pali umboni wotani umene umatsimikizira zimenezi?

23
00:01:11,440 --> 00:01:13,480
Ndiye kodi mungatani kuti muyese nambala imodzi molondola?

24
00:01:13,480 --> 00:01:17,400
Mumagwiritsa ntchito ngati malangizo anu osati maphunziro anu.

25
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:23,560
Chotero cholinga chanu pa mlingo umenewu chiyenera kukhala kuphunzira mawu, kudziŵa mfundo zazikulu

26
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:27,760
ndi kupanga mafunso ambiri kwa inu nokha, kupeza zimene simukudziwabe ndi

27
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,920
chimene ukufunabe kudziwa.

28
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:34,800
Mumathera mphindi 10 mpaka 15 mukufufuza pamalo oyamba.

29
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:39,000
Ndiyeno mumadzifunsa kuti, 'Kodi sindikumvetsabe chiyani?'

30
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:42,160
Ndipo funso limenelo ndilo khomo lanu lofikira pa mlingo wanu wachiŵiri.

31
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:44,760
Gawo lachiŵiri ndilo kufalikira kwa magwero.

32
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:47,160
Apa ndi pamene mungayambe kufufuza kwenikweni.

33
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,760
Ndiye kodi zimenezi zikuoneka bwanji?

34
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:51,880
Zimenezi zikuphatikizapo kusindikiza magwero ndi nkhani.

35
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:55,520
Amaŵerenga maphunziro athunthu m'malo moŵerenga mwachidule phunziroli.

36
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:59,120
Ikutsatira maulalo ndi zolemba ndi maumboni.

37
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,520
Pano ndi pamene inu kupita.

38
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:01,520
Kodi zimenezi n'chiyani?

39
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:03,520
Kodi zimenezi zinachokera kuti?

40
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:05,680
Tiyeni tibwerere ku chitsanzo cha zinthu zakuda.

41
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:08,640
Tsopano simukhalabe pa Google kapena TikTok.

42
00:02:08,640 --> 00:02:10,759
Mukutsegula tsamba la NASA.

43
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:12,640
Inu mukudina pa kafukufuku wotchulidwa.

44
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:18,520
Mukutsegula Kafukufuku wa Galactic Rotation Curve ndipo mukuona ma observations a

45
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,520
asayansi.

46
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:24,400
Chotero zimenezi n'zofunika kwambiri chifukwa tsopano mukuona umboni osati kungofika pamapeto.

47
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:28,080
Ndiye kodi mungatani kuti mutsegule zonse moyenera?

48
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,640
Osangowerenga tsamba n'kutseka.

49
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:33,600
Muyenera kukhala ndi ma tabu asanu kapena khumi otseguka pa chilichonse chimene mukuyang'ana.

50
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:36,400
Panopa muyenera kutsatira zimene anthu akunena.

51
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:41,760
Kotero kupita ku nkhani kuti phunziro kuti deta choyambirira, zonse kuti nthawizonse wokongola

52
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,760
Zinali zogwirizana kwambiri.

53
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:49,760
Muyenera kuika patsogolo.edu's.gov's, zolemba zofalitsidwa, zilizonse kuchokera kwa katswiri mu

54
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:50,760
m'munda.

55
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:56,000
Ndipo muyenera kudzifunsa kuti, kodi zimene ndikufunazi n'zotani?

56
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:59,799
Chifukwa ngati simungathe kuyankha funso limenelo, ndiye kuti mwangoyamba kumene.

57
00:02:59,799 --> 00:03:02,959
Ndimalowa m'chigawo chachitatu, chimene ndi kuzindikira kachitidwe.

58
00:03:02,959 --> 00:03:07,519
Ndipo ine ndikuganiza kuti ili ndi mlingo kumene choonadi kwenikweni akuyamba kuonekera chifukwa

59
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:13,040
pa mlingo uwu, cholinga chanu chachikulu ndi kuyerekezera magwero angapo ndipo inu kumvetsera

60
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:16,000
ku mapangano ndi mikangano pakati pawo.

61
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:19,880
Mukuzindikira mfundo zimene mukuziona mobwerezabwereza.

62
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:25,200
Mukuyang'ana zinthu zimene zimaonekera mobwerezabwereza pa magwero amenewo, kaya

63
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:31,480
ndi manambala kapena mafunso kapena malingaliro kapena zifukwa chifukwa zimasonyeza kuti ndi zofunika.

64
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:35,160
Tiyerekeze kuti mwawerenga zinthu zisanu ndi chimodzi zosiyana pa nkhani yamdima.

65
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:39,359
Ndipo asanu ndi mmodzi mwa iwo anati kuti galaxy kuzungulira siligwirizana ndi misa kuoneka ndi mmodzi wa iwo

66
00:03:39,359 --> 00:03:41,800
ananena kuti mwina malamulo a mphamvu yokoka ndi olakwika.

67
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:46,280
Kotero tsopano mukuona kugwirizana kukuchitika mkati mwa mutu womwewo.

68
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:51,240
Inu mukuona zodabwitsa ndi inu mukuona mkangano umene ulipo ndipo inu mukuyamba kupeza weniweni

69
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:53,280
kumvetsa zimene mukuphunzira.

70
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:56,720
Pa mlingo uliwonse, katatu molondola, mumayang'ana kuti muzigwirizana.

71
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:59,000
Ndiye kodi anthu ambiri amagwirizana pa chiyani?

72
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:01,640
Inunso muyenera kuona kusamvana.

73
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:05,720
Choncho ganizirani zimene akatswiri amasiyana pa nkhaniyi.

74
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:07,920
Muyenera kufufuza umboni umene mwapeza.

75
00:04:07,920 --> 00:04:11,880
Mungathe kusiyanitsa umboni wamphamvu ndi malingaliro.

76
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:17,039
Mukhozanso kupanga mababu atatu a maganizo kapena kuwalemba ngati mukufuna.

77
00:04:17,039 --> 00:04:22,039
Koma chimodzi ndi chidziŵitso chimene mukuchipeza chimene chili chofanana pakati pa magwero onse.

78
00:04:22,039 --> 00:04:27,680
Chimodzi ndi chidziŵitso chimene chikukambitsirana ndipo china ndi chidziŵitso chosatsimikizirika.

79
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:32,020
Ndipo mwa kuchita zimenezo, mukudziphunzitsa nokha ndi kumanga nzeru zanu

80
00:04:32,020 --> 00:04:33,720
Kuweruza nkhaniyo.

81
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:38,960
Mlingo wa kuzama ndi maziko mlingo chifukwa apa ndi pamene inu kusiya kuphunzira mfundo

82
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:41,800
ndipo mumayamba kuganiza m'machitidwe.

83
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,520
Inu mukufunsa mafunso abwino.

84
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:48,400
Mukumanga zitsanzo zamaganizo za mutu womwe mukufufuza ndipo mukuyamba

85
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:52,800
kuti agwirizanitse maganizo m'magulu osiyanasiyana a kafukufuku.

86
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:58,000
Kotero inu mukuyang'ana kwenikweni kapangidwe kumbuyo mutu wa chirichonse chimene inu kufufuza.

87
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:02,680
M'malo mofunsa kuti chinthu chakuda n'chiyani, tikufunsa mafunso ofunika kwambiri.

88
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:08,000
Timafunsa zinthu monga chifukwa chake mphamvu yokoka imagwira ntchito mwanjira imeneyi kapena ndi malingaliro ati omwe amapangidwa

89
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:13,480
m'chitsanzo chathu chilipo cha zinthu zakuda kapena chimene chingakhale chowona kwa zonsezi

90
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:15,480
kuti ndilakwe.

91
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:20,360
Mukudziphunzitsa nokha kuganiza mozama ndi kufunsa mafunso abwino, amene

92
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:22,360
ndi yofunika kwambiri pa kafukufuku.

93
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:27,880
Pa mlingo umene tikufunsa mafunso a dongosolo lachiwiri, sitifunsa chabe chiyani, koma chifukwa ndi

94
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:31,160
Nanga bwanji ngati tikumanga pa zitsanzo zathu za maganizo?

95
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:34,120
Chotero tengani pepala ndi kulijambula pamaso panu, chabwino?

96
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:37,120
Chinthu chakuda, ndi malo osungira masamu.

97
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:39,000
Zimenezi zinatsatiridwa ndi mphamvu ya mphamvu yokoka.

98
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:41,200
Sichioneka mwachindunji.

99
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:44,920
Lembani kuti muone mapu ake ndi kuyamba kugwirizanitsa.

100
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,080
Zinthu zamdima ndi sayansi.

101
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,240
Ndi cosmology.

102
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:49,280
Ndi nzeru za sayansi.

103
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:54,960
Mungatenge chidziŵitso chimene muli nacho ndi kuchikoka m'zomwe ziri umboni, zimene ziri zosatsimikizika,

104
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:58,559
zimene zili pamutuwu ndi malire a chidziwitso chathu.

105
00:05:58,559 --> 00:06:02,599
Pamene muyamba kujambula patsogolo panu ndi kupanga chitsanzo chimene muyamba kuona

106
00:06:02,599 --> 00:06:06,320
Zolumikizana zonse ndipo mumayamba kuona zoperewera zonse zomwe zikusowa.

107
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:10,159
Ndipo n'zosadabwitsa kuti zimenezi zimakuthandizani kwambiri kumvetsa nkhani imeneyi.

108
00:06:10,159 --> 00:06:13,599
Chinthu chokhudza kufufuza n'chakuti si chotsogola, koma ndi loop.

109
00:06:13,599 --> 00:06:17,719
Kotero inu kufufuza ndiyeno inu kukulitsa ndiyeno inu kuyerekeza ndiyeno inu kumanga maganizo amenewo

110
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,720
zitsanzo.

111
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:21,240
Ndipo kuchokera ku zitsanzo za maganizo amenewa mumapeza mafunso abwino.

112
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:25,640
Ndipo ndiye inu kubwereza zonse mobwerezabwereza ndi mafunso bwino inu kufufuza ndi inu kukulitsa

113
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:28,680
kachiwiri ndi inu kuyerekeza ndi inu kupanga zitsanzo zambiri.

114
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:31,720
Ndipo umu ndi mmene mumaphunzirira kuganiza nokha.

115
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:34,680
Umu ndi mmene mumayamba kumvetsa zinthu.

116
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:39,000
Ndipo n'chifukwa chake kutsatira chidwi chanu kumakhala kwamphamvu kwambiri.

